{"tid":355113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警署警長危險駕駛 官指個別事件罰6000元","createTime":"2017-08-11T04:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T10:37:36.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e77202ea828616be88de5d9abe8a5d7beffb5696","tid":355113,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"服務警隊已屆23年的45歲警署警長麥志沖，去年4月23日下午3時許於長沙灣興華街西與深盛路交界，駕駛私家車與電單車相撞，被控一項危險駕駛罪，今在九龍城裁判法院承認控罪。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指由於被告坦白認罪，考慮麥過往並無刑事記錄及熱心助人，並於警隊中擁良好聲譽，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為此乃個別事件，被判處罰款6000元</span>、停牌8個月及參加駕駛改進課程。<br />\n<br />\n法官好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904e349c76be539765f7b275463ee592f1bbf4ce","tid":355113,"uid":113921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"香港依家愈黎愈多狗官"},{"pid":"16149c5cccb9c74d708387ff93be5324ed096acc","tid":355113,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ee3cd6652db3fae843c4ece6dd4190fd9302dd9","tid":355113,"uid":134105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790fc54d78fbd6090d300bd007116044a62bbba0","tid":355113,"uid":113921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=z8dbsKDF79XyMcAhQQKKbZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7abd1923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 73歲老翁施教仁去年被揭發，自2008年起用一張寫細自己11年的身份證，成功獲聘為保安員，賺取超過50萬元薪金，去年續保安牌時遭揭發。被告早前承認以欺騙手段取得金錢及管有虛假文書等7罪，今日在屯門法院被判囚4個月。<br />\n律師求情時指，被告無案底，任職保安員時盡忠職守，曾獲警務處頒發嘉許信。裁判官則回應指：「你唔可以話呃番嚟，就話警務處嘉許佢！」最後考慮被告紀錄良好、背景及年紀等因素，裁判官輕判被告入獄4個月。"},{"pid":"53f668c06f2a9e53d0f3c96142088da85ea3cd0d","tid":355113,"uid":113921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"司法權力過大 是否有問題?"},{"pid":"75d6854b50af42bb44f7de8a934b2d9cbabaaae8","tid":355113,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b475a05607755362645b2e6d3b653cd036abc3f8","tid":355113,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"危險駕駛都判咁少"},{"pid":"ee9fd6aed4d6659e82c839eb32b7e87db8a85cb7","tid":355113,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"c80f8b7f45d85e7598d399eb0fa429e03bd67451","tid":355113,"uid":57776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"官官相衛"},{"pid":"bcf06375b487efe16f4ec8f8d3c2148f39659355","tid":355113,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>官官相衛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/yulun1978/1412318953-1411723015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fyulun1978%2F1412318953-1411723015.jpg&h=a01773ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fd70c985d1cee3df7a72e945b54ce33e6ae2ae6","tid":355113,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"有乜野唔係個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e10be23be373fc565456b586e03aad8cbf0bd52","tid":355113,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}